---
---

<section class="section features-section" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header fade-in">
      <span class="section-tag">// Features</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for performance.<br /><span class="text-muted">Designed for developers.</span></h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="features-grid stagger">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Zero Dependencies</h3>
        <p>Pure TypeScript. 12KB packed. No runtime dependencies. Ships fast.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Framework Agnostic</h3>
        <p>React, Vue, Svelte, vanilla JS. IIFE bundle for script tags.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v4M12 19v4M4.22 4.22l2.83 2.83M16.95 16.95l2.83 2.83M1 12h4M19 12h4M4.22 19.78l2.83-2.83M16.95 7.05l2.83-2.83"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Debug with why()</h3>
        <p>Trace exactly which nodes invalidated and why. No more guessing.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83M2 12h4M18 12h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Lazy + Cached</h3>
        <p>Recomputes only if dirty. Cached otherwise. Deterministic guarantees.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Cycle Detection</h3>
        <p>Cycles caught at construction time. Errors with clear messages.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M16 18l6-6-6-6M8 6l-6 6 6 6"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>TypeScript Native</h3>
        <p>Full type definitions. InputNode, ComputedNode, InspectInfo exported.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-section {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .text-muted {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--rounded-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    display: inline-flex;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
